data.title: Health Services Office (HSO)
data.text:
About the Office

The Health Services Office (HSO) is one of the units of the Campus Services Group of the University, which aims to protect the health of the Lasallian community and provide its members with essential out-patient medical and dental services.

Vision

The Health Services Office envisions delivering primary medical and dental services to promote optimum condition of mind and body of the Lasallian community.

Mission

Guided by the vision, HSO aims to provide quality health care services that will facilitate mental, physical and emotional development of students, faculty, and employees. It also endeavors to promote activities and programs to enforce proper preventive medicine and awareness of good health practices.
